---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free Macro Calculator (2026) – Calculate Daily Macronutrient Needs | BMICalc"
  description="Calculate your daily macronutrients (protein, carbs, and fats). Get a personalized macro breakdown based on your weight goals, activity, and dietary preferences."
  keywords="macro calculator, macronutrient calculator, protein calculator, carb calculator, fat calculator, keto macros, high protein diet, weight loss macros"
  canonicalUrl="https://calbmi.com/macro.html"
  bodyClass="brand-macro"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebApplication",
      "name": "BMICalc - Macro Calculator",
      "url": "https://calbmi.com/macro.html",
      "description": "Calculate your daily macronutrient needs (protein, carbohydrates, and fats) based on your weight goals, activity, and custom ratio presets (Balanced, Low Carb, Keto, High Protein).",
      "applicationCategory": "HealthApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "All",
      "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript. Requires HTML5.",
      "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0.00", "priceCurrency": "USD" },
      "aggregateRating": {
        "@type": "AggregateRating",
        "ratingValue": "4.9",
        "ratingCount": "215",
        "bestRating": "5",
        "worstRating": "1"
      }
    }
    </script>
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [{
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are macronutrients (macros)?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Macronutrients, commonly called macros, are the three primary nutrient groups your body needs in large quantities to produce energy and maintain structural integrity. They are Protein (4 calories per gram), Carbohydrates (4 calories per gram), and Fats (9 calories per gram)."
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How are daily macro requirements calculated?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "First, the calculator determines your TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure) based on your age, gender, height, weight, activity level, and weight goal. Then, it distributes these daily calories across protein, carbs, and fats based on your chosen ratio preset (e.g. Balanced: 30% protein, 40% carbs, 30% fat), converting calories into grams."
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much protein do I need per day?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "A standard recommendation for sedentary adults is 0.8 grams of protein per kilogram of body weight. However, for active individuals, lifters, or those looking to lose weight while preserving muscle, a higher intake of 1.6 to 2.2 grams of protein per kilogram of body weight (0.7 to 1.0g per lb) is recommended."
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What macro split is best for weight loss?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "For weight loss, a High Protein split (40% protein, 30% carbs, 30% fat) or a Low Carb split (30% protein, 20% carbs, 50% fat) is highly effective. High protein increases satiety and prevents muscle loss, while lower carbs help manage insulin levels and water retention."
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the ketogenic (Keto) macro ratio?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The ketogenic diet is a very high-fat, low-carbohydrate diet. The typical macro split is roughly 70-75% fat, 20% protein, and 5% carbohydrates. This drastic reduction in carbohydrates forces the body to enter a metabolic state called ketosis, burning fat for fuel instead of glucose."
        }
      }, {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I adjust my macros for muscle building?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes, building muscle (bulking) requires a caloric surplus (typically 250 to 500 calories above TDEE) combined with a Balanced (30% protein, 40% carbs, 30% fat) or High Protein macro split. The extra carbohydrates fuel intense training sessions, while the protein facilitates muscle repair and growth."
        }
      }]
    }
    </script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Calculator Section -->
  <section id="macro-calculator" class="calc-section" style="padding-top:2.5rem">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Back Link and Title -->
      <div class="calc-page-header scroll-reveal">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
          BMI Calculator
        </a>
        <div class="calc-page-title-block">
          <span class="hero-badge hero-badge-brand" style="margin:0">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 1 7 7c0 5-7 13-7 13S5 14 5 9a7 7 0 0 1 7-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg>
            Science-Based
          </span>
          <h1 class="calc-page-title">Macro <span class="hero-gradient-brand">Calculator</span></h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-grid">
        <!-- Input Card -->
        <div class="card calc-card scroll-reveal" style="--reveal-delay:0.05s">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h2 class="card-title">Daily Nutrition</h2>
            <p class="card-subtitle">Calculate protein, carb, and fat targets</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Unit Toggle -->
          <div class="unit-toggle-group" role="group" aria-label="Unit system">
            <button class="unit-btn active" id="btnMetric" onclick="setUnit('metric')">Metric</button>
            <button class="unit-btn" id="btnImperial" onclick="setUnit('imperial')">Imperial</button>
          </div>

          <form id="macroForm" class="bmi-form" novalidate>
            <!-- Age -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label" for="macroAge">Age <span class="label-hint">(15 – 100)</span></label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.58-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
                <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroAge" placeholder="e.g. 28" min="15" max="100" />
                <span class="input-unit">yrs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="form-error" id="macroAgeError"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Gender -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Gender</label>
              <div class="gender-group">
                <label class="gender-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGender" value="male" id="macroGenderMale" checked />
                  <span class="gender-card">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.58-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
                    Male
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="gender-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGender" value="female" id="macroGenderFemale" />
                  <span class="gender-card">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.58-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/><path d="M9 20h6"/></svg>
                    Female
                  </span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Height Metric -->
            <div class="form-group" id="macroHeightMetricGroup">
              <label class="form-label" for="macroHeightCm">Height</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M4 6l3 3M4 12h4M4 18l3-3M20 6l-3 3M20 12h-4M20 18l-3-3"/></svg>
                <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroHeightCm" placeholder="e.g. 175" min="100" max="280" />
                <span class="input-unit">cm</span>
              </div>
              <div class="form-error" id="macroHeightCmError"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Height Imperial -->
            <div class="form-group hidden" id="macroHeightImperialGroup">
              <label class="form-label">Height</label>
              <div class="imperial-row">
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <svg class="input-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20"/></svg>
                  <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroHeightFt" placeholder="5" min="1" max="9" />
                  <span class="input-unit">ft</span>
                </div>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                  <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroHeightIn" placeholder="9" min="0" max="11" />
                  <span class="input-unit">in</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-error" id="macroHeightImperialError"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Weight Metric -->
            <div class="form-group" id="macroWeightMetricGroup">
              <label class="form-label" for="macroWeightKg">Weight</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3a3 3 0 0 1 3 3H9a3 3 0 0 1 3-3z"/><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="15" rx="2"/></svg>
                <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroWeightKg" placeholder="e.g. 70" min="30" max="600" step="0.1" />
                <span class="input-unit">kg</span>
              </div>
              <div class="form-error" id="macroWeightKgError"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Weight Imperial -->
            <div class="form-group hidden" id="macroWeightImperialGroup">
              <label class="form-label" for="macroWeightLbs">Weight</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3a3 3 0 0 1 3 3H9a3 3 0 0 1 3-3z"/><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="15" rx="2"/></svg>
                <input class="form-input" type="number" id="macroWeightLbs" placeholder="e.g. 154" min="66" max="1300" step="0.1" />
                <span class="input-unit">lbs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="form-error" id="macroWeightLbsError"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Activity Level -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Activity Level</label>
              <div class="activity-grid">
                <label class="activity-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroActivity" value="1.2" id="macroSedentary" checked />
                  <span class="activity-card">
                    <span class="activity-dot"></span>
                    <span class="activity-text">
                      <span class="activity-name">Sedentary</span>
                      <span class="activity-desc">Desk job, little exercise</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="activity-mult">×1.2</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="activity-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroActivity" value="1.375" id="macroLight" />
                  <span class="activity-card">
                    <span class="activity-dot"></span>
                    <span class="activity-text">
                      <span class="activity-name">Lightly Active</span>
                      <span class="activity-desc">Exercise 1–3 days/week</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="activity-mult">×1.375</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="activity-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroActivity" value="1.55" id="macroModerate" />
                  <span class="activity-card">
                    <span class="activity-dot"></span>
                    <span class="activity-text">
                      <span class="activity-name">Moderately Active</span>
                      <span class="activity-desc">Exercise 3–5 days/week</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="activity-mult">×1.55</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="activity-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroActivity" value="1.725" id="macroVery" />
                  <span class="activity-card">
                    <span class="activity-dot"></span>
                    <span class="activity-text">
                      <span class="activity-name">Very Active</span>
                      <span class="activity-desc">Hard exercise 6–7 days/week</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="activity-mult">×1.725</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="activity-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroActivity" value="1.9" id="macroSuper" />
                  <span class="activity-card">
                    <span class="activity-dot"></span>
                    <span class="activity-text">
                      <span class="activity-name">Super Active</span>
                      <span class="activity-desc">Physical job + hard training</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="activity-mult">×1.9</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Goal -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Fitness Goal</label>
              <div class="goal-grid">
                <label class="goal-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGoal" value="lose2" id="mGoalLose2" />
                  <span class="goal-card">
                    <span class="goal-emoji">📉</span>
                    Weight Loss<br/><small style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.7rem">−500 kcal/day</small>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="goal-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGoal" value="lose1" id="mGoalLose1" />
                  <span class="goal-card">
                    <span class="goal-emoji">🔽</span>
                    Mild Loss<br/><small style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.7rem">−250 kcal/day</small>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="goal-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGoal" value="maintain" id="mGoalMaintain" checked />
                  <span class="goal-card">
                    <span class="goal-emoji">⚖️</span>
                    Maintain<br/><small style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.7rem">At TDEE</small>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="goal-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGoal" value="gain1" id="mGoalGain1" />
                  <span class="goal-card">
                    <span class="goal-emoji">🔼</span>
                    Lean Bulk<br/><small style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.7rem">+250 kcal/day</small>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="goal-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroGoal" value="gain2" id="mGoalGain2" />
                  <span class="goal-card">
                    <span class="goal-emoji">📈</span>
                    Gain Muscle<br/><small style="font-weight:400;font-size:0.7rem">+500 kcal/day</small>
                  </span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Macro Presets -->
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Macronutrient Split Presets</label>
              <div class="macro-preset-grid">
                <label class="macro-preset-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroPreset" value="balanced" checked />
                  <span class="macro-preset-card">
                    ⚖️ Balanced
                    <span class="macro-preset-ratios">30% P / 40% C / 30% F</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="macro-preset-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroPreset" value="highprotein" />
                  <span class="macro-preset-card">
                    🥩 High Protein
                    <span class="macro-preset-ratios">40% P / 30% C / 30% F</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="macro-preset-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroPreset" value="lowcarb" />
                  <span class="macro-preset-card">
                    🥦 Low Carb
                    <span class="macro-preset-ratios">30% P / 20% C / 50% F</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
                <label class="macro-preset-option">
                  <input type="radio" name="macroPreset" value="keto" />
                  <span class="macro-preset-card">
                    🥑 Ketogenic
                    <span class="macro-preset-ratios">20% P / 5% C / 75% F</span>
                  </span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="calc-btn-brand" id="macroCalcBtn">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 1 7 7c0 5-7 13-7 13S5 14 5 9a7 7 0 0 1 7-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg>
              Calculate Macros
            </button>

            <button type="button" class="reset-btn" onclick="resetMacroForm()">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"/><path d="M3 3v5h5"/></svg>
              Reset
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Result Card -->
        <div class="card calc-card scroll-reveal" style="--reveal-delay:0.15s" id="macroResultCard">
          <!-- Placeholder -->
          <div class="cal-placeholder" id="macroPlaceholder">
            <div class="cal-placeholder-icon" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.08);color:#8b5cf6">🥗</div>
            <p class="placeholder-text">Enter your details and click <strong>Calculate Macros</strong> to see your daily nutrient breakdown and meal recommendations</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Result Content -->
          <div class="cal-result-section hidden fade-in-up" id="macroResultContent">
            <!-- Calorie Goal Hero -->
            <div class="result-hero" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom:1.5rem">
              <div class="result-hero-label">Your Daily Target Calories</div>
              <div class="result-hero-value" id="macroCaloriesDisplay">–</div>
              <div class="result-hero-unit">kcal / day</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.775rem; color:var(--muted-foreground); margin-top:0.25rem;">
                TDEE (<span id="macroTdeeDisplay">–</span> kcal) adjusted for your goal
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Donut Chart -->
            <div class="donut-container">
              <svg class="donut-svg" viewBox="0 0 42 42">
                <!-- Base Circle -->
                <circle cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="transparent" stroke="var(--border)" stroke-width="4.2"></circle>
                <!-- Segments (Dynamic) -->
                <circle id="donutProtein" class="donut-segment" cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="transparent" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="4.2" stroke-dasharray="0 100" stroke-dashoffset="25"></circle>
                <circle id="donutCarbs" class="donut-segment" cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="transparent" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="4.2" stroke-dasharray="0 100" stroke-dashoffset="0"></circle>
                <circle id="donutFat" class="donut-segment" cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="transparent" stroke="#eab308" stroke-width="4.2" stroke-dasharray="0 100" stroke-dashoffset="0"></circle>
                <!-- Center Text -->
                <text x="50%" y="55%" class="donut-center-text" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle" font-size="3" font-weight="800">
                  MACROS
                </text>
              </svg>
            </div>

            <!-- Macros Breakdown Display -->
            <div class="macro-section" style="margin-top:0.5rem">
              <div class="macro-bars">
                <!-- Protein Row -->
                <div class="macro-row">
                  <span class="macro-name" style="color:#f43f5e; font-weight:700">🥩 Protein</span>
                  <div class="macro-bar-track"><div class="macro-bar-fill" id="mBarProtein" style="background:#f43f5e"></div></div>
                  <span class="macro-pct" id="mPctProtein" style="color:#f43f5e">0%</span>
                  <span class="macro-grams" id="mGProtein" style="font-weight:800; min-width:80px; text-align:right">–</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Carbs Row -->
                <div class="macro-row">
                  <span class="macro-name" style="color:#0ea5e9; font-weight:700">🍞 Carbs</span>
                  <div class="macro-bar-track"><div class="macro-bar-fill" id="mBarCarbs" style="background:#0ea5e9"></div></div>
                  <span class="macro-pct" id="mPctCarbs" style="color:#0ea5e9">0%</span>
                  <span class="macro-grams" id="mGCarbs" style="font-weight:800; min-width:80px; text-align:right">–</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Fat Row -->
                <div class="macro-row">
                  <span class="macro-name" style="color:#eab308; font-weight:700">🥑 Fats</span>
                  <div class="macro-bar-track"><div class="macro-bar-fill" id="mBarFat" style="background:#eab308"></div></div>
                  <span class="macro-pct" id="mPctFat" style="color:#eab308">0%</span>
                  <span class="macro-grams" id="mGFat" style="font-weight:800; min-width:80px; text-align:right">–</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Meal Breakdown Card Options -->
            <div style="margin-top:1.5rem">
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:0.5rem">
                <h3 class="section-title" style="margin:0">Meal-by-Meal Targets</h3>
                <select class="form-input" id="mealCountSelect" style="width:auto; padding:0.25rem 0.5rem; font-size:0.8rem; height:auto; margin:0;" onchange="updateMealBreakdown()">
                  <option value="3">3 Meals / day</option>
                  <option value="4" selected>4 Meals / day</option>
                  <option value="5">5 Meals / day</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="meal-breakdown" id="mealsContainer">
                <!-- Meal Cards (Dynamic) -->
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Food suggestions section -->
            <div style="margin-top:1.5rem">
              <h3 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">Recommended Food Sources</h3>
              <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:0.5rem; font-size:0.825rem">
                <div style="background:var(--muted); padding:0.75rem; border-radius:8px; border-left:4px solid #f43f5e">
                  <strong>Protein:</strong> Chicken breast, turkey, lean beef, salmon, eggs, tofu, tempeh, Greek yogurt, whey protein, lentils.
                </div>
                <div style="background:var(--muted); padding:0.75rem; border-radius:8px; border-left:4px solid #0ea5e9">
                  <strong>Carbohydrates:</strong> Oats, brown rice, sweet potatoes, quinoa, whole grain bread, fruits, vegetables, beans.
                </div>
                <div style="background:var(--muted); padding:0.75rem; border-radius:8px; border-left:4px solid #eab308">
                  <strong>Fats:</strong> Avocado, olive oil, almonds, walnuts, chia seeds, flaxseeds, egg yolks, dark chocolate, coconut oil.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Health Message -->
            <div class="health-message" id="macroHealthMsg" style="margin-top:1.25rem"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Info Section -->
      <div class="section-header scroll-reveal" style="margin-top:4.5rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem">
        <div class="section-badge" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);color:#8b5cf6;border-color:rgba(139,92,246,0.2)">Nutrition & Science</div>
        <h2 class="section-title-lg">Demystifying Macronutrients</h2>
        <p class="section-description" style="max-width:640px;margin:0.5rem auto 0;color:var(--muted-foreground)">Understand what protein, carbs, and fats do inside your body and how to balance them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-grid scroll-reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem;--reveal-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(244,63,94,0.1);color:#f43f5e">
            🥩
          </div>
          <h3 class="info-title">Protein (4 kcal/g)</h3>
          <p class="info-text">The building block of cells. Protein is essential for repairing muscular microtears from workouts, maintaining bone structure, synthesizing enzymes, and regulating satiety.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(14,165,233,0.1);color:#0ea5e9">
            🍞
          </div>
          <h3 class="info-title">Carbohydrates (4 kcal/g)</h3>
          <p class="info-text">Your body's preferred fast fuel. Carbs are converted to glucose, replenishing muscular glycogen stores and providing energy for high-intensity physical activity and brain function.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(234,179,8,0.1);color:#eab308">
            🥑
          </div>
          <h3 class="info-title">Fats (9 kcal/g)</h3>
          <p class="info-text">Crucial for hormone regulation, vitamin absorption (A, D, E, K), brain cell health, and maintaining core temperature. Fats are a dense, long-lasting energy reserve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-icon" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);color:#8b5cf6">
            ⚖️
          </div>
          <h3 class="info-title">Satiety and TEF</h3>
          <p class="info-text">Protein keeps you full longest because it has the highest Thermic Effect of Food (TEF), burning 20-30% of its calories simply during the digestive process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
